lic_en","text":"Pleasant,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"productive of enjoyment, to the eater:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easy to swallow; not attended by trouble:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"not succeeded by harm, even after its digestion."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Z, cited voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maruw^a","text_ar":"مَرُوَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"haniyoy^FA mariyoy^FA","text_ar":"هَنِيْيًا مَرِيْيًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[May it be, or Eat it, or Drink it,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with enjoyment, and with wholesome result:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with ease in the swallowing, and with quickness in digesting: &c.:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maruw^a","text_ar":"مَرُوَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"haniyoy^FA lahu *`lika","text_ar":"هَنِيْيًا لَهُ ذٰلِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"May that be productive of enjoyment to him!"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"haniyoy^FA","text_ar":"هَنِيْيًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mariyoy^FA","text_ar":"مَرِيْيًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"are of the number of epithets which are employed after the manner of inf. ns. significant of a prayer or good wish, governed in the acc. case by a verb understood. (Sb.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K"]}]}}